Sorry if this has been dealt with before, but I am having trouble building Amaya 4.2.1 from the source tarball. 
I created .../Amaya/solaris (this is on Solaris 2.7) and did "../configure --prefix=/devel/local" but it complained about not finding libwww sources. 
