Irene - This was from the source tar file, and I finally figured out what happened. 
After I unpacked the source, I started the ../configure, and at the same time I started deleting stuff from old versions of Amaya. 
I expected the libwww included with the source to be somewhere below the Amaya directory, not at the same level, so I deleted it thinking it was from an older version. 
I re-extracted, and everything configures and compiles fine. 
Thanks for the help, and sorry for my confusion. 
